<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p>Two joining fragments forming a small rough <rs type="material" key="marmor">white marble</rs> <rs type="objectType" reg="altar">altar</rs>   (<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.10</measure> × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">0.26</measure> × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="depth">0.10</measure>), with moulding above and below.</p>
</div>

<div type="description" n="text">
<head>Description of Text</head>
<p>
Inscribed on two adjacent faces (ll. 1-4 on a., 5-7 on  b) with a text that runs from one to the other.</p>
</div>

<div type="description" n="letters">
<head>Description of Letters</head>
<p>Very irregular and poorly cut; not dateable: <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.015-0.025</measure>; lunate <foreign lang="grc">Σ</foreign>, <foreign lang="grc">Ε</foreign>; cursive <foreign lang="grc">Α</foreign>.</p>
</div>

<div type="description" n="date">
<head>Date</head>
<p> <date cert="low" notBefore="0001" notAfter="0800">First century A.D. or later</date> (<rs type="criteria">nomenclature</rs>).</p>
</div>

